analysis.authors: Sergei L Kosakovsky Pond and Stephanie J Spielman
analysis.info: PogoFit, *P*rotein *G*TR *Fit*ter: Fit a general time reversible (GTR) model to a collection of training protein sequence alignments.
analysis.requirements: All alignments must be in HyPhy-format: Each file must contain a protein multiple sequence alignment and newick phylogeny. NEXUS input is not accepted.
